::DarkMouse::
In her room in the base, she stretched her arms and yawned. "Oh boy, another 
day, another computer problem to fix. What's a mouse got to do for 
excitement around here."



::GoldenEye::
She wished things had worked out for her and Dollen, but what could a girl 
do? If one has a destiny to follow, then one has to follow it. She sighed 
and waited for orders.


::Ice::
Trying to figure out just how to get her mind power undercontrol, she 
decided to start closing her mind to the thoughts of others. After all, who 
said an open mind was all that great anyway.

::Trinity::
She looked around,"Hey? Where'd everyone go?"

::Diamond::
She was bored out of her scales.  She wanted something to kill and to kill 
something soon.

::Squizzy::
In her room, studying molecular biology and transmutation in bio and 
transbio organisms.  She closed her book and decided to go to the lab to try 
out a few of her own theories.


OOC: HELLO ALL!!! I'M BACK!!! You may grovel now or run in fear. I'll be 
nice and give you that option. *big group hug* Missed you all.

Logo
